flowRoot.flowPara: GFDRR, through its Nepal DRM Country Program, has worked alongside the Government of Nepal to proactively manage disaster risks by organizing flood management projects, conducting structural surveys, and providing technical assistance for seismic-resistant modifications to buildings within Kathmandu and greater Nepal.
